Exercise 2 — Missing values


Code
d |&gt;
  select(price, carat, cut, color, depth) |&gt;
  summarize(across(everything(), ~ sum(is.na(.))))


# A tibble: 1 × 5
  price carat   cut color depth
  &lt;int&gt; &lt;int&gt; &lt;int&gt; &lt;int&gt; &lt;int&gt;
1     0     0     0     0     0


The built-in diamonds object has no NA in these columns (all counts zero).

